longBusinessSummary: Man Shing Agricultural Holdings, Inc. engages in the production and processing of fresh vegetables. Its fresh vegetables include ginger, onion, garlic, and leek. Man Shing Agricultural Holdings, Inc. also provides frozen vegetable products comprising peeled ginger, diced ginger, ginger puree cubes, ginger puree, strawberry, diced garlic, garlic puree, garlic puree cubes, diced onion, and peeled garlic. The company's customers include suppliers to supermarket chains and an ingredient producer. It markets its products in Japan, the United Kingdom, the Netherlands, and internationally. Man Shing Agricultural Holdings, Inc. was formerly known as Weifang Xinsheng Food Co., Ltd. and changed its name on August 21, 2009. The company was founded in 1998 and is based in Hunghom, Hong Kong.
